Package: aix-framework
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: AI eXploit Framework for AI/LLM security testing
 AIX is an automated security testing framework for AI/LLM endpoints.
 It provides penetration testers with tools to assess AI systems for
 vulnerabilities including prompt injection, jailbreaking, data leakage,
 and more.
 .
 Features:
  - Reconnaissance and fingerprinting of AI endpoints
  - Prompt injection attack testing
  - Jailbreak bypass techniques
  - System prompt extraction
  - Memory manipulation testing
  - RAG poisoning detection
  - Agent exploitation testing
  - OWASP LLM Top 10 vulnerability mapping
  - HTML report generation
